& [CandidateRouteInventorySpecification] is a non-mutating inventory contract
  + [source_snapshot_uuid] is bb6a059d-b8fb-4c8c-9972-e2702e12f12b
  + [manifest_uuid] is 3d3abd70-0ccd-44ce-82f7-48c83c722f65
