  + [purpose] is classify existing warm leads by admission-gate status and next route
  + [not_purpose] is new computation, proof, zero certification, branch reopening, staging, committing, broad .sop mutation, denser scans, more labels, more windows, or more offsets
  + [proof_status] is route_inventory_not_rh_evidence

& [InventoryContract] is bounded
  + [candidate_pool] is explicit residual arithmetic discrepancy, Lambda/reference overlay heat, half-plane boundary quantity, prime-power baseline, special-prime return, sparse scale-law novelty, and bridge/kernel refinement
  + [status_set] is candidate_source_request_worthy, candidate_support_only, candidate_rejected, candidate_governance_only, and candidate_not_ready
  + [required_review] is source, purpose, dense-node parentage, whole-field relevance, identity boundary, existing evidence, deterministic method, contradiction handling, restraint, exit condition, and truth boundary
  + [allowed_output] is route inventory, failed gates, support lanes, and one selected next source-request lead

  = must: cite existing record support for each warm lead
  = must: classify computation readiness separately from source-request worthiness
  = must: keep explicit residual, Lambda overlay, reference landmarks, Euler half-plane, prime-power, special-prime, sparse scale-law, and bridge-restraint identities separate
  = must: preserve paused branch decisions unless a new candidate-specific source is selected later
  - never: admit any candidate for deterministic processing in this inventory pass
  - never: treat route inventory as RH evidence or zero certification

& [CandidateRouteInventorySJS] is the specification justification trace
  + [processed_stage_set] is source_preserved, delineated, canonicalized, constraint_checked, justified, and inventory_scoped
  + [processing_result] is accepted_candidate_route_inventory_contract
  + [reasoning_result] is the measured-object gate should now be applied to the existing warm field before the workspace asks for a new candidate-specific measured object

(candidate_route_inventory) :route inventory: /warm leads, failed gates, source-request worthiness, no computation/ |proof claims|
  + [inside] is non-mutating candidate triage
  + [boundary] is no computation, no proof inference, no branch reopening, no staging, no commit
  |outside| RH proof, disproof, zero certification, critical-line authority, numerical scans, and identity fusion
